  <diagram name="Page-1" id="TBK-System-v2">
    <mxGraphModel dx="5827" dy="2437" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="0" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1400" pageHeight="1600" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="req-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;b&gt;Ticket Booking System — System Design&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;A platform to discover and purchase tickets for movies, concerts, and live events.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. Functional Requirements&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Discover events by Title, City/Location, and Date.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;View event details: seats (available/occupied), description, cast, duration, language, rating.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Select a seat and complete a booking transaction.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;b&gt;2. Non-Functional Requirements&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Support 100 Million DAU.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Availability for event search/browsing (stale reads acceptable).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Strong Consistency for seat booking (no double-booking).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;b&gt;3. Core Entities&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;User&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Event (Movie / Concert / Play)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Venue (Theater / Stadium / Arena)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Show (specific timing of event at venue)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Seat&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Booking (transaction record)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;b&gt;4. API Design&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;GET /v1/events &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;(Query Params: title, city, date) → list of events&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;GET /v1/events/{event_id} → event metadata &amp;amp; description&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;GET /v1/shows/{show_id}/seats → seat map &amp;amp; availability&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;POST /v1/bookings &amp;nbsp;(Body: event_id, show_id, seat_id) → lock seat &amp;amp; initiate transaction&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="620" width="470" x="-530" y="-120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
